== Poles of the transformation ==

The point formula_43 is called the pole of formula_44; it is that point which is transformed to the point at infinity under .

The inverse pole formula_45 is that point to which the point at infinity is transformed. The point midway between the two poles is always the same as the point midway between the two fixed points:
