== Simple Möbius transformations and composition ==

A Möbius transformation can be composed as a sequence of simple transformations.

The following simple transformations are also Möbius transformations:
* formula_59 is a translation.
* formula_60 is a combination of a homothety (uniform scaling) and a rotation. If formula_61 then it is a rotation, if formula_62 then it is a homothety.
* formula_63 (inversion and reflection with respect to the real axis)

